                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#156vb"/>
                           <desc type="DonationNote">
                              <quote xml:lang="gez">
                                 ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ዘአድ፡ ቌልቋል፡ ዘወኃቦ፡ መንፈቁ፡ ወልደ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ለቅዱስ፡
                                 ጊዮርጊስ፡ ወብእሲቱ፡ ቍስቋማዊት፡ ዘተጽሕፈ፡ በዘመነ፡ ጳጳስነ፡ አቡነ፡ ቂርሎስ፡ ወንጉሥነ፡ ሰብአ፡
                                 ጋድስ፡ ወቄስ፡ ገበዙ፡ ክፍለ፡ ጊዮርጊስ። ወምስለ፡ ጸሐፊሐ፡ ኃጥእ፡ ዘንድግል፡[sic] ትኩኖሙ፡ ምርፋቅ፡
                                 ምስለ፡ ኂሩያን፡ ደቂቅ፡ [n.l.]ኩድኖሙ፡ ልብሰ፡ ጽድቅ፡ ኅብረ፡ ሰን[n.l.]ቅ፡ ዘይትባደር፡
                                 እምብሩር፡ ወወርቅ። ዘሰረቃ፡ ወዘፈተቃ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡ በቃለ፡ ፻፫፲ወ፰ርቱዓነ፡ ሃይማኖት።</quote>
                              <quote xml:lang="en"/> Mention of the donors, <persName ref="PRS11079WaldaG">Walda Giyorgis</persName> and his wife
                                 <persName ref="PRS11080Qusqam">Qwusqwāmāwit</persName>. The book
                              was written during the time of Metropolitan <persName ref="PRS8032Qerellos">Qerǝllos [Qirǝllos]</persName> (in tenure
                              1816-28), and daǧǧāzmāč 
                              <persName ref="PRS8265Sabagadi">Sabāgādis
                                 [Sabʾā Gādis]</persName>, governor of <placeName ref="LOC6569Tegray">Tǝgrāy</placeName> from 1822 to 1831 (here
                              called nǝguś), and qes gabaz 
                              <persName ref="PRS11078Kefla">Kǝfla
                                 Giyorgis</persName> of <placeName ref="INS0097AQG">Qǝddus Giyorgis
                                 ʿĀddi Qolqwāl [Qwelqwal]</placeName> church (also mentioned in the
                              supplication formulas throughout the text).</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#15va #24ra"/>
                           <desc type="Supplication">Supplication formulas mentioning the scribe
                                 <persName role="scribe" ref="PRS11077Zadengel">Za-Dǝngǝl</persName>
                              and the donors.</desc>
                        </item>
                     </list>
